{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"ca75d1451c","title":"在中共中央政治局常委会议上的讲话","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"207f97355c","index":0,"year":1935,"month":6,"day":29,"articleId":"ca75d1451c"}],"tags":[{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"id":"e23dcf99fa","name":"发言","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji7-2","name":"毛泽东全集第7卷(2)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji7-2.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji7-2":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"f9a53b9352","type":"paragraph","text":"在中共中央政治局常委会议上的讲话！","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"ca75d1451c"},{"id":"4944218dc4","type":"paragraph","text":"（1935年6月29日）","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"ca75d1451c"},{"id":"ad670952fb","type":"paragraph","text":"日军进攻北平，明显地要侵占华北。现在各帝国主义国家的冲突在中国表现为军阀间的矛盾。日本帝国主义想把蒋介石完全控制在自己手下。党对时局应有表示，应发表文件。要在部队中宣传反对日本帝国主义，反对放弃华北，这最能动员群众。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"ca75d1451c"},{"id":"dbdc7027f7","type":"paragraph","text":"[1]1935年6月29日，中共中央政治局常委会议在两河口召开。这是毛泽东在听取博古（秦邦宪）关于华北事变、日军向北平进攻的情况报告后","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"ca75d1451c"},{"id":"4e3b8851bb","type":"paragraph","text":"1935年6月至8月，中共中央政治局先后在两河口、沙窝、毛儿盖多次召开会议，讨论红军落脚问题。图为两河口会议旧址。","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"ca75d1451c"}],"page":{"id":"c1ce7b806e","publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"ca75d1451c","start":186,"end":187}}}},"__N_SSG":true}